overview: Out-and-proud comedian Kate Clinton celebrates her 25th anniversary of performing in this blend of stand-up footage, behind-the-scenes clips, interviews, footage of Clinton reading from her book, What the L?, photos and more. With her trademark cutting political satire and clever one-liners, Clinton always puts on a dynamic and hilarious show. Lily Tomlin, Melissa Etheridge, Billie Jean King and other celebrities join in the fun.
title: Kate Clinton: The 25th Anniversary Tour
